{"tid":361251,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"網上行呢間野當人傻","createTime":"2017-08-16T03:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T08:58:50.000Z","uid":130253,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4439bc5808e86df0f754e400763b935ddc226109","tid":361251,"uid":130253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"我冇交三個月上網費...我知我問題<br />\n之後上星期五打上去問交番錢係咪開得番<br />\n佢就開始講話已經終止左服務<br />\n交左錢都話冇得開番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定要星期三師傅上門重裝番先有上網<br />\n之後叫我換個新約先有得上番網<br />\n咁就好啦，約左番裝<br />\n之後我星期日又突然用得番<br />\n覺得怪怪地<br />\n用到今日（星期三）師傅打黎話裝上網<br />\n我覺得奇怪話唔洗，佢就講左句：「你架機停架喇喎」<br />\n我而家就比佢依句搞到打上1000問佢咩事"},{"pid":"9d0e720b8d1b53084a5eccf060986aa60c537007","tid":361251,"uid":96983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:39:31.000Z","msg":"人地條RULES 寫到明有權CUT你就要攪一大輪安裝嫁啦<br />\n自己問題 仲聲大夾惡"},{"pid":"bff069c15eba724f3791ad83e2e76904cf6e9df6","tid":361251,"uid":8246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"自己3個月無比錢仲惡人先告狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58805e8815baaa37b41d396c875d3ea166c61346","tid":361251,"uid":132041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d26b12d54e8e7063df8d9fbe44f4b7dddd0d5be","tid":361251,"uid":140330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7bca1ced15846945504ab84d097d7c9f9d654e9","tid":361251,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"我都試過，其實上網無問題架，佢係cut 左你個流量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfe40bf6ec338600882f42b86c2a53991108cc8","tid":361251,"uid":54104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過，其實上網無問題架，佢係cut 左你個流量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" c